Title: Carbon Cannondale SuperX Ultegra
text: Carbon fiber 2016 Cannondale SuperX cyclocross / gravel bike with Ultegra groupset. 56 cm, I've had riders from 5'9" to 6'2" fit comfortably. 2017 model, has typical cosmetic wear and tear (pictured) but is mechanically sound. Ultegra shifters and derailleurs, hydraulic disc brakes. I'm the original owner and have the original manual. Currently on nearly new Specialized Pathfinder tires, great for urban and gravel riding. No room to keep this and two other bikes, so I'm consolidating.

Title: Youth Kona Makena
text: 11" youth Kona bike

Title: Rocky Mountain disc brake bike
text: 18" aluminum frame front suspension disc brake 24 speed Rocky Mountain Flare. New comfort seat, chain, brake pads, brake cables and shifter cables. Tuned and rides great. Tires are really good.

Title: Kona Dawg Primo
text: Well cared for Kona Dawg Primo with a fox Talus 32 front and float rp23 rear full suspention mountain bike. Medium/large-  Im running a long stem and am 6ft1.  Rides great for shorter riders with stock stem as well.  Raniaco computer, new grips - ready for the summer season.  907five 0045 nine 9

Title: Trek 800 bike
text: 17" frame 21 speed trek 800.  New cassette, chain, front derailleur, shifters, brake pads, brake cables and shifter cables.  Tuned and rides nice.  Tires are excellent.  Comes with front and rear fenders, drink holder, cargo rack, cargo bag.  A perfect commuter

Title: Schwinn High Timber Aluminum bike
text: Aluminum frame 21 speed front suspension Schwinn mountain bike.  New shifters, freewheel, chain, rear derailleur, brake pads, brake cables and shifter cables.  Tuned and rides nice.
